author: Rob Braxman Tech
description:
Performing an Internet search isn't as simple as Googling, or even asking Siri. It's time to understand the privacy invasions possible in search engines and to create a safe solution. Searching is one of the most used ways of profiling users. This video will show alternatives that provide privacy safe options while still giving good search results.
